        <item>
            <title>Version 0.3.0</title>
            <description>
                <ul>
<li>Preliminary full-screen support (<a href="https://github.com/qvacua/vimr/pull/98">#98</a>)</li>
<li>Bugfix: Preview window does not work well with multiple tabs (<a href="https://github.com/qvacua/vimr/issues/131">#131</a>)</li>
<li>Added support for folders in <code>Open Quickly</code> (<a href="https://github.com/qvacua/vimr/issues/120">#120</a>): use <code>/</code>, eg <code>fi/class</code> for <code>first/folder/containing/some/class</code></li>
<li>Added horizontal scroll to file browser (<a href="https://github.com/qvacua/vimr/issues/119">#119</a>)</li>
<li>Restructured the menu: Note that some keyboard shortcuts changed (<a href="https://github.com/qvacua/vimr/issues/93">#93</a>)</li>
</ul>
            </description>
